Expectations and Goals

The course aims to provide linear algebra background to students for taking advanced classes or performing research in metallurgical and material engineering and other engineering disciplines.

Course Materials

Textbook

[1] Lay, D. C., Lay, S. R. and McDonald J. J. (2016). Linear Algebra and Its Applications. Pearson.

Optional Materials

[2] Leon, S. J. (2015). Linear Algebra with Applications. Pearson.

[3] Strang, G. (2003). Introduction to Linear Algebra. Wellesley-Cambridge Press.

Assignment Policy
